#CHIP YM2203
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2203 (OPN) FM Channels Test
;
; The YM2203 has 3 FM channels (identical structure to YM2149, but with
; full FM synthesis and 3 independent SSG channels).
;
; Tests FM functionality across all 3 channels:
; - Channel 1: Basic melody
; - Channel 2: Different timbre
; - Channel 3: Harmony
;
; Validates FM register writes and tone generation.

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1: Melody (C4, D4, E4)
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Channel 2: Second voice (offset)
g3 . a3 . b3 .

r4

; Channel 3: Harmony (thirds)
e4 . f4 . g4 .

r4

; All channels together
c4 & g3 & e4 .

r2

#END
